Quality Assurance_40 CFR Part 51.363 



An ongoing quality assurance program shall be implemented to discover, correct and prevent fraud, waste, and abuse
in the program. The program shall include covert and overt performance audits of the inspectors, audits of station
and inspector records, equipment audits, and formal training of all state I/M enforcement officials and auditors.
